---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="Esettanulmányok — 90 nap, +1.1M Ft / hó | BoxBook"
  description="Hogyan használják a BoxBookot valódi autókozmetikák: AutoGloss Stúdió (Budapest, +47% foglalás), Detail Garage Debrecen (induló szalon), Crystal Wash Group (5 telephely)."
  canonical="/esettanulmanyok"
>
  <section id="esettanulmany" class="relative bg-ink-50 border-y border-ink-200">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-5 lg:px-8 py-24 lg:py-32">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-10 items-end mb-12">
        <div class="lg:col-span-7 fade-up">
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-white ring-1 ring-ink-200 text-ink-700 px-3 py-1 text-[11px] font-bold tracking-widest uppercase">
            <i data-lucide="chart-no-axes-combined" class="w-3 h-3"></i>
            Esettanulmány
          </span>
          <h1 class="mt-5 text-4xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold tracking-tightest text-balance leading-[1.02]">
            90 nap, <span class="grad-text-strong">+1.1 M Ft havi bevétel.</span>
          </h1>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-5 fade-up" style="transition-delay: 80ms">
          <p class="text-ink-600 text-lg text-pretty">
            Egy belvárosi szalon valós számai a BoxBook foglaló + Növekedés marketing-csomag bevezetése után. <span class="text-ink-500 text-sm">(illusztratív, anonimizált eset — saját ügyfelünk engedélyével)</span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <article class="fade-up rounded-3xl bg-white ring-1 ring-ink-200 shadow-[0_30px_80px_-30px_rgba(9,9,11,0.15)] overflow-hidden">
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-6 p-6 lg:p-10 border-b border-ink-100 bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-ink-50/60">
          <div class="lg:col-span-7">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 flex-wrap">
              <span class="grid place-items-center w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl grad-bg text-ink-900 font-extrabold text-xl tracking-tightest shadow-[0_8px_20px_-6px_rgba(132,204,22,0.4)]">AG</span>
              <div>
                <div class="font-extrabold text-ink-900 tracking-tighter2 text-xl">AutoGloss Stúdió</div>
                <div class="text-xs text-ink-500 flex items-center gap-3 mt-0.5 flex-wrap">
                  <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1"><i data-lucide="map-pin" class="w-3 h-3"></i> Budapest, V. ker.</span>
                  <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1"><i data-lucide="boxes" class="w-3 h-3"></i> 3 mosóállás</span>
                  <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1"><i data-lucide="users" class="w-3 h-3"></i> 2 munkatárs</span>
                  <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1"><i data-lucide="calendar" class="w-3 h-3"></i> 2025 ősz indulás</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="lg:col-span-5 flex flex-wrap gap-2 lg:justify-end items-center">
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-full bg-leaf-50 ring-1 ring-leaf-200 text-leaf-700 px-3 py-1.5 text-xs font-bold"><i data-lucide="sparkles" class="w-3.5 h-3.5"></i> BoxBook Pro</span>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-full bg-cyan-50 ring-1 ring-cyan-200 text-cyan-700 px-3 py-1.5 text-xs font-bold"><i data-lucide="megaphone" class="w-3.5 h-3.5"></i> Növekedés csomag</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 divide-x divide-y lg:divide-y-0 divide-ink-100">
          <div class="p-6 lg:p-8">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-ink-500 font-extrabold"><i data-lucide="calendar-clock" class="w-3.5 h-3.5"></i> Foglalás / hó</div>
            <div class="mt-4 flex items-end justify-between gap-3">
              <div>
                <div class="text-[10px] text-ink-400 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Előtte</div>
                <div class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-ink-500 tracking-tightest line-through decoration-2 decoration-ink-300">180</div>
              </div>
              <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="w-5 h-5 text-leaf-600 mb-2"></i>
              <div class="text-right">
                <div class="text-[10px] text-leaf-700 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Utána</div>
                <div class="text-3xl font-extrabold grad-text-strong tracking-tightest">264</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-3 inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-full bg-leaf-50 text-leaf-700 ring-1 ring-leaf-200 px-2 py-0.5 text-[11px] font-extrabold">
              <i data-lucide="trending-up" class="w-3 h-3"></i> +47%
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 lg:p-8">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-ink-500 font-extrabold"><i data-lucide="banknote" class="w-3.5 h-3.5"></i> Havi bevétel</div>
            <div class="mt-4 flex items-end justify-between gap-3">
              <div>
                <div class="text-[10px] text-ink-400 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Előtte</div>
                <div class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-ink-500 tracking-tightest line-through decoration-2 decoration-ink-300">2.4M</div>
              </div>
              <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="w-5 h-5 text-leaf-600 mb-2"></i>
              <div class="text-right">
                <div class="text-[10px] text-leaf-700 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Utána</div>
                <div class="text-3xl font-extrabold grad-text-strong tracking-tightest">3.5M Ft</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-3 inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-full bg-leaf-50 text-leaf-700 ring-1 ring-leaf-200 px-2 py-0.5 text-[11px] font-extrabold">
              <i data-lucide="trending-up" class="w-3 h-3"></i> +1.1M Ft
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 lg:p-8">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-ink-500 font-extrabold"><i data-lucide="bell-off" class="w-3.5 h-3.5"></i> No-show ráta</div>
            <div class="mt-4 flex items-end justify-between gap-3">
              <div>
                <div class="text-[10px] text-ink-400 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Előtte</div>
                <div class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-ink-500 tracking-tightest line-through decoration-2 decoration-ink-300">18%</div>
              </div>
              <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="w-5 h-5 text-leaf-600 mb-2"></i>
              <div class="text-right">
                <div class="text-[10px] text-leaf-700 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Utána</div>
                <div class="text-3xl font-extrabold grad-text-strong tracking-tightest">6%</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-3 inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-full bg-leaf-50 text-leaf-700 ring-1 ring-leaf-200 px-2 py-0.5 text-[11px] font-extrabold">
              <i data-lucide="trending-down" class="w-3 h-3"></i> −67%
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 lg:p-8">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-ink-500 font-extrabold"><i data-lucide="star" class="w-3.5 h-3.5"></i> Google értékelés</div>
            <div class="mt-4 flex items-end justify-between gap-3">
              <div>
                <div class="text-[10px] text-ink-400 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Előtte</div>
                <div class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-ink-500 tracking-tightest"><span class="line-through decoration-2 decoration-ink-300">4.1</span></div>
                <div class="text-[10px] text-ink-400">(47 review)</div>
              </div>
              <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="w-5 h-5 text-leaf-600 mb-4"></i>
              <div class="text-right">
                <div class="text-[10px] text-leaf-700 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Utána</div>
                <div class="text-3xl font-extrabold grad-text-strong tracking-tightest">4.7</div>
                <div class="text-[10px] text-leaf-700 font-bold">(89 review)</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-3 inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-full bg-leaf-50 text-leaf-700 ring-1 ring-leaf-200 px-2 py-0.5 text-[11px] font-extrabold">
              <i data-lucide="trending-up" class="w-3 h-3"></i> +0.6 ★ · +89%
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-6 lg:gap-10 p-6 lg:p-10">
          <div class="lg:col-span-7">
            <h2 class="font-extrabold text-ink-900 tracking-tighter2 text-xl">Mi történt 90 nap alatt</h2>
            <ol class="mt-5 space-y-4">
              <li class="flex gap-4">
                <span class="grid place-items-center w-9 h-9 rounded-xl bg-ink-900 text-white font-extrabold text-sm shrink-0">1</span>
                <div>
                  <div class="font-bold text-ink-900 tracking-tighter2 text-sm">Hét 1–2: alap-felmérés &amp; bevezetés</div>
                  <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-ink-600 leading-relaxed">Onboarding: meglévő 412 vendég és 388 jármű importja Excel-ből. Árazási mátrix összeállítása szolgáltatás × kategória bontásban. Foglalási flow tesztelése a tulajdonossal.</p>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-4">
                <span class="grid place-items-center w-9 h-9 rounded-xl bg-ink-900 text-white font-extrabold text-sm shrink-0">2</span>
                <div>
                  <div class="font-bold text-ink-900 tracking-tighter2 text-sm">Hét 3: Google Business profil &amp; helyi keresés</div>
                  <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-ink-600 leading-relaxed">GMB optimalizálás (fotók, szolgáltatás-leírás, nyitvatartás), Google Ads helyi kampány — „autókozmetika 5. kerület” + 12 hasonló kulcsszóra.</p>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-4">
                <span class="grid place-items-center w-9 h-9 rounded-xl bg-ink-900 text-white font-extrabold text-sm shrink-0">3</span>
                <div>
                  <div class="font-bold text-ink-900 tracking-tighter2 text-sm">Hét 4–6: Meta Ads + Before/After kreatívok</div>
                  <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-ink-600 leading-relaxed">Heti 2 új kreatív a BoxBook fotó-galériájából. Pixel beállítás, retargeting a Google Adsből érkező látogatókra. 4-ből 1 lead foglalássá vált.</p>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-4">
                <span class="grid place-items-center w-9 h-9 rounded-xl grad-bg text-ink-900 font-extrabold text-sm shrink-0 shadow-[0_8px_20px_-6px_rgba(132,204,22,0.4)]">4</span>
                <div>
                  <div class="font-bold text-ink-900 tracking-tighter2 text-sm">Hét 7–9: vendég-újraaktiválás &amp; vélemény-szerzés</div>
                  <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-ink-600 leading-relaxed">A 60+ napja nem járt 156 vendéghez kampány-email + személyre szabott kupon. 38 vendég visszatért. Minden COMPLETED foglalás után auto-rate kérés Google-re.</p>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-4">
                <span class="grid place-items-center w-9 h-9 rounded-xl grad-bg text-ink-900 font-extrabold text-sm shrink-0 shadow-[0_8px_20px_-6px_rgba(132,204,22,0.4)]">5</span>
                <div>
                  <div class="font-bold text-ink-900 tracking-tighter2 text-sm">Hét 10–13: kihasználtság-optimalizálás</div>
                  <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-ink-600 leading-relaxed">Aktív/passzív fázisok élesítése a polírozás-szolgáltatásnál → +12% kapacitás ugyanaz a 2 alkalmazott mellett. Bérletek bevezetése (5+1 mosás), 47 vásárlás.</p>
                </div>
              </li>
            </ol>
          </div>

          <div class="lg:col-span-5 space-y-5">
            <div class="rounded-2xl bg-ink-900 text-white p-5 relative overflow-hidden">
              <div class="absolute -top-12 -right-12 w-36 h-36 grad-bg rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-30"></div>
              <div class="relative">
                <div class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-white/55 font-extrabold">Havi bevétel — 6 hónap</div>
                <svg viewBox="0 0 400 200" class="mt-3 w-full" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <defs><linearGradient id="caseBar" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1"><stop offset="0" stop-color="#a3e635"/><stop offset="1" stop-color="#06b6d4"/></linearGradient></defs>
                  <g stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.08)" stroke-width="1">
                    <line x1="30" y1="40" x2="395" y2="40"/>
                    <line x1="30" y1="80" x2="395" y2="80"/>
                    <line x1="30" y1="120" x2="395" y2="120"/>
                    <line x1="30" y1="160" x2="395" y2="160"/>
                  </g>
                  <line x1="178" y1="20" x2="178" y2="160" stroke="rgba(132,204,22,0.5)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="4 3"/>
                  <rect x="148" y="6" width="60" height="14" rx="7" fill="#84cc16"/>
                  <text x="178" y="16" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="9" font-weight="800" fill="#0a0a0a" text-anchor="middle">BOXBOOK</text>
                  <rect x="40" y="106" width="38" height="54" rx="3" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.15)"/>
                  <rect x="86" y="112" width="38" height="48" rx="3" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.15)"/>
                  <rect x="132" y="100" width="38" height="60" rx="3" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.15)"/>
                  <rect x="186" y="86" width="38" height="74" rx="3" fill="url(#caseBar)"/>
                  <rect x="232" y="64" width="38" height="96" rx="3" fill="url(#caseBar)"/>
                  <rect x="278" y="48" width="38" height="112" rx="3" fill="url(#caseBar)"/>
                  <rect x="324" y="42" width="38" height="118" rx="3" fill="url(#caseBar)"/>
                  <g font-family="sans-serif" font-size="9" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.55)" font-weight="600">
                    <text x="59" y="178" text-anchor="middle">Jún</text>
                    <text x="105" y="178" text-anchor="middle">Júl</text>
                    <text x="151" y="178" text-anchor="middle">Aug</text>
                    <text x="205" y="178" text-anchor="middle">Sze</text>
                    <text x="251" y="178" text-anchor="middle">Okt</text>
                    <text x="297" y="178" text-anchor="middle">Nov</text>
                    <text x="343" y="178" text-anchor="middle">Dec</text>
                  </g>
                  <g font-family="sans-serif" font-size="9" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.45)" font-weight="700">
                    <text x="59" y="100" text-anchor="middle">2.4M</text>
                    <text x="105" y="106" text-anchor="middle">2.3M</text>
                    <text x="151" y="94" text-anchor="middle">2.5M</text>
                  </g>
                  <g font-family="sans-serif" font-size="10" fill="#a3e635" font-weight="800">
                    <text x="205" y="80" text-anchor="middle">2.9M</text>
                    <text x="251" y="58" text-anchor="middle">3.2M</text>
                    <text x="297" y="42" text-anchor="middle">3.4M</text>
                    <text x="343" y="36" text-anchor="middle">3.5M</text>
                  </g>
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-ink-200 p-6">
              <i data-lucide="quote" class="w-6 h-6 text-leaf-600"></i>
              <p class="mt-3 text-ink-800 leading-relaxed text-base">
                „Két dolog változott. Az egyik: a bevételünk fele. A másik: a stresszünk negyede. Korábban este 9-kor még a holnapra szóló időpontokat egyeztettem telefonon. Most a vendégeink maguktól foglalnak, és <b>én meg végre tudok családot is.”</b>
              </p>
              <div class="mt-4 flex items-center gap-3">
                <span class="grid place-items-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-ink-900 text-white text-xs font-extrabold">PB</span>
                <div>
                  <div class="font-bold text-ink-900 tracking-tighter2 text-sm">Péter B.</div>
                  <div class="text-[11px] text-ink-500">tulajdonos · AutoGloss Stúdió</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="border-t border-ink-100 bg-ink-50/60 px-6 lg:px-10 py-5 grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 text-xs">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-ink-700"><i data-lucide="users-round" class="w-4 h-4 text-leaf-600"></i><b class="text-ink-900">+184 új vendég</b></div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-ink-700"><i data-lucide="ticket" class="w-4 h-4 text-leaf-600"></i><b class="text-ink-900">47 bérlet</b> eladva</div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-ink-700"><i data-lucide="repeat" class="w-4 h-4 text-leaf-600"></i><b class="text-ink-900">38 visszahozott</b> vendég</div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-ink-700"><i data-lucide="clock-9" class="w-4 h-4 text-leaf-600"></i><b class="text-ink-900">~1.5 hó</b> megtérülés</div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <div class="mt-6 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-5">
        <article class="fade-up rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-ink-200 p-6 lg:p-7">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="grid place-items-center w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-leaf-50 text-leaf-700 ring-1 ring-leaf-200 font-extrabold text-base tracking-tightest">DG</span>
            <div>
              <div class="font-extrabold text-ink-900 tracking-tighter2">Detail Garage</div>
              <div class="text-[11px] text-ink-500 flex items-center gap-2 mt-0.5">
                <span>Debrecen</span> · <span>1 mosó</span> · <span>1 fős</span> · <span>Induló csomag</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-ink-700 leading-relaxed">
            Pista papír-naptárból váltott BoxBookra. A „mostantól csak online foglalsz” email-kampány után <b class="text-ink-900">60 nap alatt 130 új online foglalás</b>, <b class="text-ink-900">70 új vendég</b>. A telefon nem szól, a feleség hangulata stabil.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-5 grid grid-cols-3 gap-2">
            <div class="rounded-lg bg-ink-50 ring-1 ring-ink-200 p-3">
              <div class="text-[9px] uppercase tracking-widest text-ink-500 font-bold">Foglalás</div>
              <div class="mt-1 font-extrabold text-ink-900 tracking-tighter2">+130</div>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-lg bg-ink-50 ring-1 ring-ink-200 p-3">
              <div class="text-[9px] uppercase tracking-widest text-ink-500 font-bold">Új vendég</div>
              <div class="mt-1 font-extrabold text-ink-900 tracking-tighter2">70</div>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-lg bg-leaf-50 ring-1 ring-leaf-200 p-3">
              <div class="text-[9px] uppercase tracking-widest text-leaf-700 font-bold">Telefon</div>
              <div class="mt-1 font-extrabold text-ink-900 tracking-tighter2">−72%</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <blockquote class="mt-5 text-[13px] text-ink-700 leading-relaxed italic">
            „Először 1 hónapig csak néztem a foglalások listáját. Aztán ráéreztem a ritmusra.”
            <span class="block mt-1 not-italic text-[11px] text-ink-500">— István K., tulaj</span>
          </blockquote>
        </article>

        <article class="fade-up rounded-2xl bg-ink-900 text-white p-6 lg:p-7 relative overflow-hidden" style="transition-delay: 80ms">
          <div class="absolute -top-12 -right-12 w-40 h-40 grad-bg rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-30"></div>
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="grid place-items-center w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-white/10 ring-1 ring-white/15 text-leaf-400 font-extrabold text-base tracking-tightest">CW</span>
              <div>
                <div class="font-extrabold tracking-tighter2">Crystal Wash Group</div>
                <div class="text-[11px] text-white/55 flex items-center gap-2 mt-0.5">
                  <span>5 telephely</span> · <span>18 mosó</span> · <span>Hálózat csomag</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-white/80 leading-relaxed">
              Korábban Excel-tábla és WhatsApp-koordináció 5 helyen. BoxBook Hálózat tier + lánc-szintű hűségpont indulása után <b class="text-white">6 hónapon belül +28% visszatérő-rate</b>, és először látták egy képernyőn mind az 5 szalon teljesítményét.
            </p>
            <div class="mt-5 grid grid-cols-3 gap-2">
              <div class="rounded-lg bg-white/5 ring-1 ring-white/10 p-3">
                <div class="text-[9px] uppercase tracking-widest text-white/55 font-bold">Visszatérő</div>
                <div class="mt-1 font-extrabold tracking-tighter2 text-white">+28%</div>
              </div>
              <div class="rounded-lg bg-white/5 ring-1 ring-white/10 p-3">
                <div class="text-[9px] uppercase tracking-widest text-white/55 font-bold">Bevétel</div>
                <div class="mt-1 font-extrabold tracking-tighter2 text-white">+22%</div>
              </div>
              <div class="rounded-lg bg-leaf-400/10 ring-1 ring-leaf-400/30 p-3">
                <div class="text-[9px] uppercase tracking-widest text-leaf-400 font-bold">Adminóra</div>
                <div class="mt-1 font-extrabold tracking-tighter2 text-white">−18 / hó</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <blockquote class="mt-5 text-[13px] text-white/85 leading-relaxed italic">
              „A 4. szalon megnyitásánál nem kellett új rendszert tanulni. Csak felvettük a listához.”
              <span class="block mt-1 not-italic text-[11px] text-white/55">— Anna M., operációs vezető</span>
            </blockquote>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-4 fade-up">
        <p class="text-sm text-ink-600">A saját szalonod is hasonlót látna?</p>
        <a href="#" data-contact-source="AUDIT_REQUEST" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-ink-900 text-white px-5 py-3 text-sm font-extrabold hover:bg-ink-800 transition-colors">
